title.label: Beware! They are charging us for new levels!

content.label:
After all this time you finally come out with an update with some new levels. Then when I start to play it asks me to confirm the in game purchase. What's up with that! If you are not creating free updates with more levels like everyone else, then just tell us. Don't say that there are 15 new levels and forget to tell us we have to pay for them. 

Perhaps the developers should create a entirely new game with 50 plus levels. I would buy that.

title.label: A lot of care went into this

content.label: You can tell the developers spent a lot of time on this. The rewind feature makes it perfect. I just hope all future updates are free as opposed to creating an entirely new game (e.g. Beyond Beyond Ynth).
